content: My Perfect Fit is a designer couture label. Every piece of clothing has a unique feature that makes the bride and bridesmaid feel and look their best on their special days. Their designers are a dependable and talented designer who ensures customer satisfaction by using high-quality fabrics and keeping the bridegroom-to-vision be's and requirements in mind. Bridal Lehengas and Light Lehengas are among the styles available. Their team of experts does arrangements for their client’s specific desires and visions, helping to ensure that their wedding is everything they hoped for. They work with various price points without compromising service quality to serve a diverse core audience. They have been doing this work for a very long time and hence have a lot of experience.

Sri Janani Catering Service is a catering company serving all over Chennai. Sri Janani Catering Service started catering for wedding and other events. With countless clients, ranging from public to private companies, Sri Janani Catering Service gained a reputation for elegant presentations and impressive services. Be assured of the fact that the food is prepared & served under hygienic conditions and all rates are inclusive of top-class service, crockery & cutlery. Cuisines offered: North Indian South Indian Chinese Desserts Bengali

Wedding Mela is an end to end wedding planning brand located in Chennai. They have dedicated professionals with the best skills to create something new and unique. Efficiency and success is a habit of this passionate team who put their heart and soul in preparing for the big day with all details attended to perfection. They have experience of more than 5 years. Their decor ideas and designs are definitely a source of inspiration that will surely make your venue look outstanding from every angle. They have covered many international weddings. Areas Covered: Chennai

At Glowwed Films, they capture the love & wedding stories of modern Indian couples. Based in Mumbai, they cover events all over India. By the team Glowwed Films Out of passion, love for photography and knack for handling clients & extensive events, Glowwed Films was brought into existence. started our journey in 2015, since then we have captured countless weddings and pre-weddings.

Ms.Richa is an upscale bridal makeup artist based out of the city of dreams, Mumbai, in the north-western Indian state of Maharashtra, offering all-around wedding makeup solutions. She is a talented artist giving beautiful makeovers to her patrons on the most important occasion of their lives. The team of artists is passionate about their work and put in hard yards which are quite evident in the way they offer their services to their clients with enormous dedication. The proficient artists work relentlessly to produce unmatched results and their portfolio is brimming with vibrant colors. The expert professionals are highly proactive to all their clientele's needs. The talented artists are highly skilled and are always on the top of the list for people seeking bridal makeup services in the locality.

Sanjana Thakur, the Indian designer has strong love for design and crafts. It was her dream to build a made in India label that supports our heritage craftmanship and bring forward our rich culture and traditional arts.An Architect by profession, her drive and passion for intricate hand embroidery and love for fashion led to the development of the label Sanjana Thakur.Her signature style shows designs inspired by life and nature. She is a curious person and the innovation in design, textiles and embroidery reflects in her outfits.

Image Photoshop is a wedding photography company based in the city of dreams, Mumbai. Sam Jagdale is the creative director and lead photographer here and he is truly a rare and gifted candid photographer. For him, the world is a canvas and the camera is his brush through which he paints true emotions, personality, and intensity in each of his subjects of the wedding shoot.
Makeup, Hair(Buns/Braids/Any Hairstyle), Draping, Lashes

The Kanjeevaram Saree is one of those wedding staples that every girl wants in her bridal wardrobe, especially if you're a Mumbai or Marathi girl who's had a long lived love affair with sarees. Infact, is bridal bliss even complete without a Kanjivaram Saree? Years have gone by but the popularity of this attire only seems to be peaking. From celebrity designers making them to Bollywood stars wearing them, the Kanjivaram Saree is certainly an attire that you too ought to have on your bucket list, along with other inspiring top notch bridal wear that you could browse on the MerryWedding
description: How do I know what's trending

content: Armour Bespoke is a menswear designer store located in Pune. They provide high-quality clothing ensembles for all grooms to wear on their wedding day. They are well-known for their beauty, high-quality fabrics, and exceptional craftsmanship. Their fundamental knowledge is combined with skills to create a lovely set of sherwanis for you. Their designs respect Indian heritage and customs, and their team of experts will curate your costume with the finest precision and correctness. They provide extremely elegant and luxurious bespoke menswear that is appropriate for your wedding day.

At Dakshin Flavours they know that every event requires the best service with ingenuity & creativity. They deliver the best of authentic, delicious and mouth-watering cuisines. They have very reasonable rates for both non-vegetarian as well as vegetarian menus and would provide any cuisine according to the demands and needs of their clients. They are a catering and planning company based out in Chennai. Cuisines Offered: North Indian South Indian Desserts

We grew up reading storybooks, Dreaming of our favorite characters, Enacting our treasured chapters. " Each event will spin a story which will be timeless like the tales from the past. The tailored tale takes care of every detail from the concept to production perfection . We help you with 1.Venue exploring 2.Creating a look book, 3.Setting mock-ups 4.2D/3D Visualing for your event

SASH is a brand that provides bespoke designer fashion men's groom wear, suits, jackets, formals, casual, evening wear, accessories, customised wardrobe management and also personal shopping. Based in the city of Pune, SASH is lead by the couple Sanket and Shilpa who are passionate about what they do and love getting clients what they need for their special day! They are experts at getting groom wear ready from scratch to finish in a way that leaves the client delighted! If their profile gives you a positive vibe, be sure to give them a ring! Specialization: Sherwanis Suits and Tuxedos Indo-Western Outfits Bandhgalas Kurta Pyjama Sets Waistcoats and Nehru Jackets Groom Accessories

The Accord ODC is a Chennai based team of experienced and passionate chefs for whom cooking is not just a job but an art. They believe that good food makes happy faces. Ever seen a person being sad while eating good food? Obviously not! They aim to give your guests an experience they'll cherish for the rfest of their lives. They ensure the quality and hygiene of the food that they cook without compromising with the taste.

Based in Chennai, Marriage Knot is a wedding planning service provider that guarantees that the most important day of your life is well prepared and the happiest day of your life. Weddings are the most important events in the lives of the bride and groom since they mark the beginning of a new chapter. However, arranging an Indian wedding flawlessly is no simple undertaking. Your quest for a talented and imaginative group of experienced wedding planners who can guarantee that your wedding and all of the events surrounding it will be unique can end right here.

CamLens Photography is a wedding photography and videography company situated in Ganesh Nagar, Mumbai. Photographs have a way of informing us what is special and what should always be treasured and cherished. So, if you are a soon-to-be married couple looking for a skilled photographer, your quest ends with CamLens Photography. It is the creation of Kamlesh Parmar, an excellent photographer who catches each minute to precision.
Makeup, Hair(Buns/Braids/Any Hairstyle), Draping, Lashes, Nail Polish

Neeta Lulla is an Indian Fashion Designer and Stylist based out of Mumbai,India. She has been designing wedding outfits since 1985 and became really popular after she designed clothes for the lead actresses in the movie Devdas. Also she has been awarded for designing costumes for various movies ever since her she has been a part of this industry. Hailed as the “Czarina of Indian Fashion”, Neeta Lulla is an icon in the fashion industry.

Movie'ing Moments is a team of young photographers and filmmakers who are passionately inclined towards storytelling in the most visually stunning way. The founder, Vaaibhav Singvi, and his passion for filmmaking, love for weddings, and joy in creating stories by freezing moments led to the establishment of this venture. This group of wedding photographers at Movie’ing Moments aim to capture the beautiful ceremonies, rituals and the culture in all its essence and rich, vibrant glory. Their insatiable desire in making marriages the most wonderful event ensure supremacy in their work across every aspect.
Makeup, Hair(Buns/Braids/Any Hairstyle), Draping, Lashes

It was her dream to build a made in India label that supports our heritage craftmanship and bring forward our rich culture and traditional arts.An Architect by profession, her drive and passion for intricate hand embroidery and love for fashion led to the development of the label Sanjana Thakur.

Sandhu - The Royal Stitch is one of the most renowned men's wear designer boutiques of Amritsar serving customers since 1975. Our philosophy is to make sure you look good! Tailored to perfection, using the finest fabrics, we are a one-stop-shop for buying high-end quality outfits for all your nuptial ceremonies, from diverse styles to patterns and colours to materials. Made to measure tailoring will enable you to design and construct the perfect wedding attire for your big day that is a reflection of your ideas and character! Our designs are highly inspired from our royal heritage and are a true representation of our Indian customs and traditions.

Established in 1992 with a view to provide a wide range of menus with a great focus on presentaion and service. They are the recognised and professional outdoor caterers and service providers and have over 20 years of experience in fulfilling the catering needs of marriages. Being associated with WMG for a period of 3 years, Hiring them can be best option ever.

there is a business called Grace Events & Management that organises weddings. It provides a wide range of services to superbly plan and carry out your wedding. A wedding requires careful planning and execution because it is one of the best and most important days of a person's life and must be handled appropriately. Grace Events & Management excels in wanting to comprehend what clients want and planning everything accordingly.
